Flash address map (WROOM)
0x1000   -> bootloader
0x8000   -> partitions
0xE000   -> boot_app0
0x10000  -> esp32_marauder_v1_11_0_20260310_old_hardware.bin
Verify Marauder is running
After flashing, open the TERMINAL button in esp.huhn.me, press EN (reset button) on the board. You should see:
ESP-IDF version is: v5.x.x
Failed to mount SD Card  <- NORMAL, no SD card attached
GPS Not Found           <- NORMAL, no GPS module
Type 'help' to confirm all commands are available. SD card and GPS errors are expected and harmless.
